NO. 126 KIDICH NYASAYE (God's day of Rest)

1. Kidich Nyasaye, ndalo mamor, 
Meduru paro Jakonywa; 
To tinende waweyo tich 
Kaka Nyasaye nowachonwa

Paruru kawuono 
Kaka Nyasaye nochweyo piny; 
Ka nochweyo polo gi piny, 
Koro eka nodiro En; 
Wan bende tinende, 
Wachokre diro gi Nyasaye.

2. Nyasaye nowachonwa niya; 
Atieko gwedho Sabato; 
To wadwaro mondo Nyasaye 
Omednwa gweth mare tinde.

3. Keturu chunyu kuom Yesu, 
To en nomiu kuwe mare; 
Nitie wang'yo moro bende, 
To en modwaro witowa

